{"tid":1055633,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)忌日快樂/死亡無限LOOP1-2","createTime":"2019-03-10T16:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T19:38:26.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2a97e8eeedcb4b845d5cc48d66314deee9b27688","tid":1055633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=5ee293b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=c8ddde2e\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=a5e6c5b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/f8/Happy_Death_Day_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ff8%2FHappy_Death_Day_Poster.jpg&h=57840a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.女大學生崔兒&middot;吉曼於她生日當天的9月18日星期一早上，因昨晚派對狂歡喝醉而在一間男生宿舍裡醒來，面前只有將她扶持回來睡覺的同學卡特&middot;戴維斯。崔兒立刻離開回到她的姐妹會宿舍，隨後度過一個自我為中心、不屑他人的一天生日；她無視父親和她一起用餐的邀請，將室友蘿莉親手為她做的紙杯蛋糕扔掉，還和她的醫科教授葛雷格搞地下師生戀。當晚，崔兒獨自前去姐妹會即將在兄弟會宿舍開的派對時，被一個生日音樂盒引入一條地下隧道後，突然被一個面戴大學球隊吉祥物貝比面具的不明殺手襲擊並殺害<br />\n<br />\n2.在首集事件一天後，崔兒&middot;吉曼出乎意料地重新進入時間輪迴，並在發覺她的朋友們現在通通被捲入後決定逃離。當她發現原本的殺手蘿莉&middot;史賓格勒遭到他人謀殺後，崔兒必須面對新的殺手並揭曉對方的真實身份以永遠逃離時間輪迴<br />\n<br />\n12 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=bb33debb\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=0d0aa406\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f412fdfe9dc72cf82b010da66e4b6f0dc6f58cec","tid":1055633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T16:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25453fbd231406126628280aa1706e568b33c935","tid":1055633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:05:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90d1fd448e71aaeaeed26bf6df2a441e03369b0","tid":1055633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40acefd5b9afd09e72136c7c2855c8f230e3acc","tid":1055633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8fd9683d248b144ada18b4a7c287b1a983b137","tid":1055633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T19:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505e9ce71e398bd14debf227e8872b72a37c3636","tid":1055633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T19:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}